# Project: Vibe Coder Prompt Refiner Tool

## Tech Stack Standards
- Framework: Next.js 16 (App Router)
- Component Library: shadcn/ui (React 19 compatible)
- Styling: Tailwind CSS 4.0 (Using modern inline configuration, no legacy directives)
- Architecture: Server-Driven UI with isolated client components for interactivity

## Optimization & Multi-Device Compatibility
- Strict exclusion of `node_modules`, `.next`, and build artifacts from local background indexers.
- Modularized file boundaries so that the codebase can be built seamlessly across low-spec and high-spec machines.